      • isVersionNumberInOSName

        public boolean isVersionNumberInOSName()
        Returns whether the version number of any OS.Version of this OS is included in The {@code os.name} system property. For example, this is true for Windows, as The {@code os.name} system property.contains the version number in its value, e.g. "Windows 8.1" or "Windows 10".
        Returns:
        true if the version number of any OS.Version of this OS is included in The {@code os.name} system property. or otherwise false.
